<paragraph blockId="67.[151,1436,972,1460]" pageId="67" pageNumber="68">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,282,972,997]" pageId="67" pageNumber="68">Taxonomy.</emphasis>
Analysis of 
<collectionCode LSID="urn:lsid:biocol.org:col:14498" box="[425,473,973,997]" httpUri="http://biocol.org/urn:lsid:biocol.org:col:14498" name="University of Coimbra Botany Department" pageId="67" pageNumber="68">COI</collectionCode>
barcodes for the subgenus 
<emphasis box="[780,968,972,997]" italics="true" pageId="67" pageNumber="68">Alpigenobombus</emphasis>
shows 
<taxonomicName box="[1053,1166,972,997]" class="Insecta" family="Apidae" genus="Bombus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="67" pageNumber="68" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="validus">
<emphasis box="[1053,1166,972,997]" italics="true" pageId="67" pageNumber="68">B. validus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
to be a species separate from 
<taxonomicName box="[214,324,1008,1033]" class="Insecta" family="Apidae" genus="Bombus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="67" pageNumber="68" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="nobilis">
<emphasis box="[214,324,1008,1033]" italics="true" pageId="67" pageNumber="68">B. nobilis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, contrary to the interpretations of Williams 
<emphasis box="[830,881,1008,1033]" italics="true" pageId="67" pageNumber="68">et al</emphasis>
. (
<number box="[905,964,1008,1032]" pageId="67" pageNumber="68" value="2009.0">2009</number>
) and An 
<emphasis box="[1074,1125,1008,1033]" italics="true" pageId="67" pageNumber="68">et al</emphasis>
. (
<number box="[1149,1209,1008,1032]" pageId="67" pageNumber="68" value="2011.0">2011</number>
), which were based solely on morphology.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
